<section>
	<h2 class="page-header" id="description">Description</h2>
	<p>Borders can be added to grids or other elements in order to separate or call attention to a section of content.</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2 class="page-header" id="options">Border options</h2>
	<p>There are 4 borders that can be added:</p>
	<ul>
		<li><code>.brdr-tp</code></li>
		<li><code>.brdr-rght</code></li>
		<li><code>.brdr-bttm</code></li>
		<li><code>.brdr-lft</code></li>
	</ul>

	<section>
		<h3>Adding borders to a grid cell</h3>
		<p>Borders can be added to a grid cell. Since grids have a left and right gutter, the border will be appear on outside edge of the gutter.</p>

		<ul class="row list-unstyled">
			<li class="col-md-3 brdr-tp">
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md">Top border</p>
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-3 brdr-tp&quot;&gt;</code></p>
			</li>

			<li class="col-md-3 brdr-rght">
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md">Right border</p>
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-3 brdr-rght&quot;&gt;</code></p>
			</li>

			<li class="col-md-3 brdr-bttm">
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md">Top bottom</p>
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-3 brdr-bttm&quot;&gt;</code></p>
			</li>

			<li class="col-md-3 brdr-lft">
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md">Left border</p>
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-3 brdr-lft&quot;&gt;</code></p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h3>Adding borders to content</h3>

		<ul class="row list-unstyled">
			<li class="col-md-3">
				<p class="brdr-tp"><span class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md">Top border<br />
				<code>&lt;p class=&quot;brdr-tp&quot;&gt;</code></span></p>
			</li>

			<li class="col-md-3">
				<p class="brdr-rght"><span class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md">Right border<br />
				<code>&lt;p class=&quot;brdr-rght&quot;&gt;</code></span></p>
			</li>

			<li class="col-md-3">
				<p class="brdr-bttm"><span class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md">Bottom border<br />
				<code>&lt;p class=&quot;brdr-bttm&quot;&gt;</code></span></p>
			</li>

			<li class="col-md-3">
				<p class="brdr-lft"><span class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md">Left border<br />
				<code>&lt;p class=&quot;brdr-lft&quot;&gt;</code></span></p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h3>Adding multiple borders to the same element</h3>

		<ul class="row list-unstyled">
			<li class="col-md-3 brdr-tp brdr-lft">
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md"><span class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md">Top and left border<br />
				<code>&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-3 brdr-tp brdr-lft&quot;&gt;</code></span></p>
			</li>

			<li class="col-md-3 brdr-bttm brdr-rght">
				<p class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md"><span class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md">Bottom and right border<br />
				<code>&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-3 brdr-bttm brdr-rght&quot;&gt;</code></span></p>
			</li>

			<li class="col-md-6">
				<div class="brdr-tp brdr-rght brdr-bttm brdr-lft">
					<p class="mrgn-tp-md mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-lft-md mrgn-rght-md">Top, right, bottom and left border<br />
					<code>&lt;p class=&quot;brdr-tp brdr-rght brdr-bttm brdr-lft&quot;&gt;</code></p>
				</div>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<div class="row wb-eqht mrgn-tp-lg mrgn-bttm-xl">
